## ⚠️ EDUCATIONAL USE ONLY - IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER

This software contains intentionally malicious code designed for educational
and security awareness purposes only.

**BY USING THIS SOFTWARE, YOU AGREE TO:**

1. **Educational Purpose Only**: This software is intended solely for learning
   about MCP (Model Context Protocol) security vulnerabilities in controlled
   environments.

2. **No Production Use**: Never deploy this software or any derivative work to
   production systems or environments where it could cause harm.

3. **Responsible Disclosure**: Use knowledge gained from this workshop to
   improve security, not to exploit systems.

4. **No Liability**: The authors and contributors bear NO responsibility for
   any misuse of this software or damages caused by its deployment outside
   controlled educational settings.

5. **Compliance**: Ensure your use complies with all applicable laws and
   regulations in your jurisdiction.

**WARNING**: The MCP server in this repository performs intentionally malicious
actions including reading sensitive files, simulating data exfiltration, and
modifying configuration files. These actions are for demonstration purposes
only and are clearly logged for educational transparency.

If you plan to use this workshop in a professional or institutional setting,
ensure you have proper authorization and inform all participants of the
educational nature of the malicious code.
